### GET root (public)
GET http://localhost:5179/
Accept: application/json

###

### POST /signup (valid - requires token)
POST http://localhost:5179/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

{
  "name": "Abdulla",
  "email": "abdulla@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "MySecurePassword123"
}

### POST /signup (valid - no token)
POST http://localhost:5179/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Abdulla",
  "email": "abdulla@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "MySecurePassword123"
}


###

### POST /signup (missing fields - should fail)
